{"tid":1948613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防武肺病毒影響國安　美軍情報小組進駐核戰碉堡","createTime":"2020-03-29T06:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:24:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbac84579f22a5e5fbb4b70641137b978ed91f68","tid":1948613,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20200329/640_60e15fad9cc2a4cf97eb0f896cafeae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20200329%2F640_60e15fad9cc2a4cf97eb0f896cafeae1.jpg&h=517e9040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國軍方啟用位於夏延山地下的「備用指揮中心」核碉堡。翻攝「The Drive」<br />\n<br />\n美國的武漢肺炎（COVID-19）確診病例已超過中國，成為全球最多。為了避免疫情蔓延影響國安，美國軍方已啟用位於科羅拉多州的「夏延山地底碉堡」（Cheyenne Mountain bunker）。相關人員將在地底隔離數月，嚴密監控是否有敵軍趁機對美國發動攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n新聞網站「The Drive」和《每日郵報》報導指出，美國軍方最近已啟用位於夏延山地底的「備用指揮中心」核碉堡。美國北方司令部（U.S. Northern Command）和北美防空司令部（NORAD）指揮官歐蕭尼西上將（Terrence O'Shaughnessy）說：「為了確保我國能在疫情下保衛國土，我們的指揮和監控小組分成多班次和不同隊伍，部分人員已開始在夏延山的空軍基地工作，另外還成立了第3支小組。」<br />\n <br />\n據報導，萬一夏延山碉堡內也出現確診病例，歐蕭尼西所說的「第3支小組」便會在另一個地點運作。<br />\n <br />\n歐蕭尼西說：「北方司令部和北美防空司令部的專業監控人員已離開他們的家，向家人告別，和其他人隔離，以確保能繼續為了我們的家園時時刻刻保持警戒。」<br />\n <br />\n「The Drive」報導指出，夏延山軍方綜合設施位於堅固花崗岩下方約610公尺。每棟獨立設施的面積約為2公頃，設施入口設置重達25噸的防爆大門。美國政府當時耗時4年設置此地下碉堡，目的就是因應可能遭受的核彈攻擊威脅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20200329/640_6269dd886d3aa1f5409ab2190fc676ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20200329%2F640_6269dd886d3aa1f5409ab2190fc676ab.jpg&h=f917d970&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n夏延山地底碉堡可獨立運作，擁有自行發電設施、暖氣及冷卻系統，也有獨立的水源供給。媒體形容，在全球遭受疫情肆虐下，此地點顯然成為最好的「避疫所」。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200329/ABHXARR332LFFVSIAIZHCM7ZXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200329%2FABHXARR332LFFVSIAIZHCM7ZXE%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=09e39d87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200329%2FABHXARR332LFFVSIAIZHCM7ZXE%2F&h=6bcaec8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200329/ABHXARR332LFFVSIAIZHCM7ZXE/</a>"},{"pid":"3f93a830432fd1e6a8498520d55225a293d9ee52","tid":1948613,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814306069e3fcc5f31bec8863f74f3b9f09ee4ae","tid":1948613,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"mount weather?"},{"pid":"bc4b5dbb78c499f725078cd8e3f59571fb89074a","tid":1948613,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"可能過多排會改名做vault(number?) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1611df09807d27521d15c0ecd49978e3e6dfc373","tid":1948613,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"根本係戰爭狀態mode"},{"pid":"2364db084b97eb4426b4dc790c8c2829e9ae84a0","tid":1948613,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way<br />\nRuin CCP"},{"pid":"1a8b36116a6410b55e5c13b5fde6fc9c372929a7","tid":1948613,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LK9OACV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLK9OACV.png&h=d035bcb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cbfa2af3181d07c26624b067869829c00117752","tid":194